Nice modern Buddhist Temple. Very bright and clean.

Fu Hui Buddhist Cultural Centre conducts large scale Earth Store King Bodhisattva prayer ceremony annually lasting for about 26 days in total. Usually is from the  1st day of 7th lunar month until 26th day of the 7th lunar month. It is located in the same building as Buddhist Welfare Service.

This temple use to be very good and it is also where my late parent tablet are placed. I was the on that day to pray my late parents and I couldn't find my late parents tablets so I asked the counter service staff to help me. the were so rude and reluctant to help me and after given both my parent name they told me they couldn't find. I'm very disappointed with the service of this temple. And I've even told my brother not to donate to this temple anymore.
